members.member:
Get the PXR information of a pattern. name of the pattern structure containing PXR information. C++ API returned false///
Detailed Description:
This API returns a structure with PXR information. This data exposes pxrName, information about Domains such as DisplayOrder, LinkMode and LinkPins and also contains information about pattern Trigger table
C# Code Example var pxrFileInfo = await wrappedSdkPattern.GetPxrInfoAsync(patternName);
C++ Original HdmtApi Signature GetPxrInfo(const std::string& patternName, PxrFileInfo& pxrFileInfo);

